pages.text: Big Hex can use magic to harness storm power and create powerful spells.
The bulb on Florafox’s tail is said to hold special healing power!
The air around Arctursus is always cold because his fur is made of ice that can’t melt!
Diveodile’s natural magic ability is boosted by the Warden pendant it wears.
While moving underground, he can reach speeds of up to 100 mph!
